---
title: Speedy Teriyaki Sesame Chicken with Tenderstem®  Broccoli and Basmati Rice
description: It takes less than 25 minutes to make this Speedy Teriyaki Sesame Chicken. Widely used in Japanese barbecue dishes, teriyaki's name comes from the Japanese 'teri', meaning 'shine' and 'yaki' meaning fried or grilled.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R39_W37_UK_C4204-22576-10_Main_low_2-ad39bc68.jpg
